WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:09.200
Realistically, anybody is a candidate for Morpheus8 Burst Deep — anyone who's

00:09.200 --> 00:14.000
looking to improve skin elasticity and tighten things up.

00:14.000 --> 00:18.160
Results appear pretty quickly; most show up in the first month or so, and

00:18.160 --> 00:20.000
continue to improve from there.

00:20.000 --> 00:24.320
Morpheus8 Burst Deep is different from other technologies — typical

00:24.320 --> 00:27.320
microneedling reaches up to two millimeters in depth.

00:27.320 --> 00:31.320
Burst technology reaches up to eight millimeters and targets

00:31.320 --> 00:32.920
